    <text>
        <body>
            <div>
                <opener><salute>Dr Sir</salute></opener>
                <p>The sooner y<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> corrections come the better for fear of
                    the abolition of franks.</p>
                <p>It was impossible to have a large scale for <bibl type="authorial"><title ref="bi0209">my map</title></bibl>. Pray cd you get (for my own use) the
                    Eastern Coast put in right; if I sent you the map with that part omitted.
                        <persName ref="pe0156">M<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Low</persName> ought
                    in Justice to send me his materials <rs ref="ar0204">drawings</rs> &amp;c if he
                    does not mean to go on with his work. Hint it I beg to him. Please to forward
                    the inclosed <hi rend="underline">Post Paid</hi>. I inclose y<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> old bill. Pray make a new one with the debt for
                    the book you was so kind as to buy. &amp; the postage of the inclosed.</p>
                <closer><salute>adieu <lb/>y<hi rend="superscript">rs</hi> truely</salute>
                    <signed><persName ref="pe0232">T Pennant</persName></signed>
                <dateline><placeName ref="pl0001">Downing</placeName> March 29<hi rend="superscript">th</hi> 1777.</dateline></closer>
                <postscript>
                    <p>I set out on Monday. inclose y<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> next <lb/>to
                            <persName ref="pe0015">Sir Roger Mostyn. B<hi rend="superscript">t</hi></persName>
                        <placeName ref="pl0734">Bruton Street</placeName>
                        <lb/><placeName ref="pl0699">London</placeName>.</p>
                </postscript>
            </div>
            <div>
                <p><address>
                        <addrLine>To</addrLine>
                        <addrLine>M<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Paton</addrLine>
                        <addrLine>Custom House</addrLine>
                        <addrLine>Edinburgh</addrLine>
                    </address></p>
                <p><handShift/>7/2</p>
            </div>
        </body>
